<div class="page-eyebrow">Protocol Guide</div>
  <h1>How to lower ApoB &#8212;<br><em>what actually works.</em></h1>
  <p class="guide-hero-sub">ApoB is the most accurate predictor of cardiovascular disease risk available without imaging. This guide covers every evidence-based intervention &#8212; dietary, lifestyle, and pharmacological &#8212; ranked by effect size, with realistic expectations for how much each one moves the needle.</p>
</section>

<div class="guide-meta">
